## Slide to power on  


Power on - After power on the SPA, turn on the system automatically. Or while the screen is off, touch to wake up the screen and follow the prompts to slide the icon and then power on. After power on the SPA, wait for 1 minute before operating the panel.  


## 0  


Power Off - Touch this button to power off.  


When the system is power off, all loads will be turned off. When the system is power on, the screen will light up, the thermostat function will start, and the heat pump will run automatically to control the water temperature to the set temperature degree. The circulation pump is on. The sanitizing functions is turn on manually. In the following icons, only the underwater disinfection icon and light icon can be operated by touch.  

